Hi Vijay,

If 

   a
  b  = c

then 

  log (c) = a
     b

So if 
  
  log (0) = a
     b

then 

   a
  b  = 0

but there's no way to raise a number to any power and end up with
zero.  So log(0) is undefined. 

Does this help? 

